<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 15:54:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>比特币两个月来首次跌破 68,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-02/bitcoin-tumbles-below-70-000-for-first-time-in-two-months</link><description>由于对伊朗冲突的担忧以及主要持有者 Strategy Inc. 的抛售削弱了投资者的兴趣，比特币近两个月来首次跌破 68,000 美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i4GS.zfV6DYs/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 07:07:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-02/bitcoin-tumbles-below-70-000-for-first-time-in-two-months</guid></item><item><title>来自 AZ 的重要加密术语列表</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-06-02/crypto-slang-meaning-fomo-dats-rug-pull-sniping-diamond-hands-and-more</link><description>&lt;p&gt;从空投到僵尸，这里有一个关于区分普通人和真正信徒的术语和行话的简明指南。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/imQaskDwwnGA/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2026 09:00:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-06-02/crypto-slang-meaning-fomo-dats-rug-pull-sniping-diamond-hands-and-more</guid></item><item><title>施纳贝尔表示，欧洲央行对稳定币的最佳反应是数字欧元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-01/best-ecb-response-to-stablecoins-is-digital-euro-schnabel-says</link><description>执行委员会成员伊莎贝尔·施纳贝尔表示，稳定币对金融稳定和货币政策构成了许多风险，欧洲央行的最佳应对措施是确保公共资金仍然是该系统的支柱。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iKefa6MWRRWQ/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 00:10:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-01/best-ecb-response-t